title: [+ chancellor +] arrested
subtitle: Coup plot averted, or coup in motion?
new-page: true
view-if: kpd_influence >= ((army_force+sa_force+sh_force)/10) and (interior_kpd_seen or (kpd_influence*rfb_force) >= 250) and kpd_influence >= (papen_chancellor_timer*3) and (rfb_force >= sa_force+army_force+sh_force) not spd_in_government and not spd_caretaker and chancellor_party != "KPD"
tags: event
max-visits: 1

= Crisis in the Capital!

One morning, when [+ chancellor +] is meeting with his ministers, a warrant is produced for him and his entire cabinet. All access to Berlin is suspended as they are arrested, and, over national radio, it is proclaimed that [+ chancellor +]'s government had been planning an illegal self-coup to destroy German democracy.

- @naive: Wow, I can't believe [+ chancellor +] would do that!
- @streetsmart: This  is clearly a putsch.

@naive

Yeah, it's crazy, right? Thankfully we have the police forces to protect us from coups like this. It's a good thing the communists reformed them to be loyal to the republic!

- @rigged_election: New emergency elections have been scheduled.

@streetsmart

It is plain to see that this is a communist coup. Having secured so much influence over state institutions, and then deprived the management of those institutions, they seek to wrestle back power.

- @rigged_election: New emergency elections have been scheduled.
- @soviet_germany.resist: Together, we can stop the [? if president != "Thälmann" and president != "Münzenberg" and chancellor_party != "KPD" : [+ kpd_leader +] ?][? if president == "Thälmann" or president == "Münzenberg" : [+ president +] ?][? if chancellor_party == "KPD" and president != "Thälmann" and president != "Münzenberg" : [+ chancellor +] ?] putsch!

@rigged_election
on-arrival: workers_kpd += rfb_force; workers_kpd += kpd_influence; unemployed_kpd += kpd_influence; unemployed_kpd += (rfb_force*2); new_middle_kpd += kpd_influence; rural_kpd += kpd_influence; time_to_election = 3; president = "Wirth"; old_middle -= 5; rural -= 5; workers += 5; catholics -= 5; {!
Q.workers_other *= (1-(Q.rfb_force/100));
Q.new_middle_other *= (1-(Q.rfb_force/100));
Q.rural_other *= (1-(Q.rfb-force/100));
!}
call: set_next_election_time

New elections have been called, under the oversight of communist-aligned forces.